  "id": "019ce002-bd22-7c30-89ce-9ddf6e8d0f01",
  "content": "# Dashboard Tier 1 Design Spec (2026-03-12)\n\n## Navigation Structure\n```\nHeader: [Brand] [Health Pulse ●●●] [Tabs] [Scope] [Clock]\nTabs:  Traces*  |  Agents  |  RAG  |  Logs  |  Graph\n         ↑ default landing (architecture topology)\n```\n\nNew tabs: Agents, RAG. Enhanced: Traces (topology as navigation hub), Header (health pulse).\n\n## Tab: Traces (landing, enhanced)\n- Module nodes become navigation portals\n- Agent module click → detail panel + \"View all agents →\" link to Agents tab\n- Merge module click → detail panel with live queue, inline one-click retry buttons (no confirmation)\n- RAG module click → detail panel + \"Open RAG explorer →\" link to RAG tab\n- Other modules → existing behavior (spans + events)\n\n## Tab: Agents (new)\n- Grid of agent cards: name, ID, heartbeat indicator (green=active, amber=stale, red=orphaned), session count, entry count, last seen\n- Click card → expand: session timeline (Active→Committing→Merging→Closed), per-session entries, contribution sparkline\n\n## Tab: RAG (new)\n- Query Explorer (top): input box → POST /api/rag/ask → answer + pipeline trace\n- Pipeline Trace (bottom): waterfall bars (Retrieve→Augment→Generate), token gauge (used/budget), source panel with similarity scores\n- Cross-nav: clicking RAG span in Traces topology navigates here with trace pre-loaded\n\n## Header: Health Pulse\n- Three dots next to service pills (knowledge integrity, merge health, system)\n- Green/amber/red per category\n- Click → sidebar transforms to Health Detail panel\n- Health panel: expandable check rows (stale, broken chains, orphans, dangling edges, cycles), counts, severity badges, \"Run check\" button\n- Auto-runs on first click, caches, re-runs every 60s while open\n- Click away → sidebar reverts to config\n\n## Sidebar Modes\n- Tab strip: Config | Health\n- Default: Config panel\n- Health dots clicked: Health detail panel\n\n## API Calls\n- Agent cards: GET /api/agents (5s poll)\n- Agent sessions: GET /api/agents/:id/sessions (on expand)\n- Merge queue: GET /api/merge/queue (3s with traces)\n- Merge retry: POST /api/merge/retry (on click)\n- RAG trace: POST /api/rag/ask (on submit)\n- Health checks: POST /api/reason/corvia (on open, then 60s)\n\n## Build Order\n1. Agents tab (self-contained, validates new tab pattern)\n2. Merge queue inline in Traces detail panel\n3. RAG tab\n4. Health pulse in header + sidebar",
  "source_version": "mcp",
